column1: How do I call an agent
column2: To call an agent, you can can double press the call button, or say, "Call an agent."

column1: How do I turn on privacy mode
column2: To turn privacy mode on and off during a call, you can press on the call button once. Privacy mode disables your audio and video so that the agent cannot hear or see anything on your end.

column1: What is the customer care number
column2: You can reach our caring customer care team at 858 876 2472 between 6am to 6pm Pacific Time on weekdays, and between 9am to 2pm Pacific Time on weekends.
